                    </a>
                    <div class="property-content">
                        <div class="price mb-2"><span>Exploring Dubai’s Luxury Real Estate Market</span></div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="d-block mb-2 text-black-50">Dubai is synonymous with luxury, and its real estate market is no exception. Over the years, Dubai has become one of the top destinations for luxury real estate, attracting high-net-worth individuals, investors, and celebrities from all over the world. From stunning penthouses with city views to waterfront villas on private islands, the city offers something […]</span>

                            <div class="specs d-flex mb-4 mt-4">
                                <span class="d-block d-flex align-items-center me-3">
                                    <i class="fa fa-calendar"></i>
                                    <span class="caption">&nbsp;December 16, 2024</span>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-end">
                                <a href="property-single.html" class="btn btn-primary py-2 px-3">Read More</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 mt-3 text-center">
                <button class="btn btn-primary py-2 px-3">VIEW MORE PROPERTY</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



